KreateTableOne = function(x, ...){
  t1 = tableone::CreateTableOne(data=x, ...)
  t2 = print(t1, quote=TRUE)
  rownames(t2) = gsub(pattern='\\"', replacement='', rownames(t2))
  colnames(t2) = gsub(pattern='\\"', replacement='', colnames(t2))
  return(t2)
}
